cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on face recognition using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also introduces a new loss function to improve the discriminative capability of deep features, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves experiments and evaluations on two popular face recognition benchmark datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
